# Auto-detected from file content when a file is uploaded. Still required for metadata-only BOM artifacts (type: BOM with downloadLinks but no uploaded file), since there is nothing local to inspect. Will be removed once download-link content inference is available.
	bomFormat: String
	storedIn: String
